Definition.Description: Get to the results quicker with the SPC Accelerator Add-on.
Definition.Document:
SPC Accelerator Add-on

Get to the results quicker with the SPC Accelerator Add-on. 

Step 1: Load your signals and relevant conditions. Here will we will load Viscosity, or Grade Code Condition, and the times where our process is In-Control. (starting point)

Step 2: Put these inputs into the Add-on tool. 

Step 3: View the 3 worksheets created, including Histogram, Control Chart, and Run Rules. 

 

SPC Add-on: Control Chart and Nelson Run Rules
